{"tid":1328704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民先係最撚分化","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:15:29.000Z","uid":64181,"like":15,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0eeb258ef8707cb797947b8297effe8e78eb7f9c","tid":1328704,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"等睇連登販民線人同支持者屈我話熱狗，獨派<br />\n<br />\n7.1 擋人衝立法會，連前線都屌佢地出賣香港人<br />\n新城市投訴又影人帶鐵通<br />\n依家個勢大好，個南亞之父又冇鳩啦啦推個單次移交搞到失哂焦<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你地咪撚再分化，成日開口話兄弟爬山，屌你老母係咁拉後腿，仲用舊時技倆派一班泛民打手出黎屈毛屈人熱狗，食撚屎啦，最分化就係你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dedc9488b14695450b38750cf6323a5b262ec7","tid":1328704,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:03:00.000Z","msg":"當睇唔到條撚樣得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n全場除左聽日暴動真係冇撚用"},{"pid":"82a4dca587d705f68e478d69afd4fc65224856db","tid":1328704,"uid":137604,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主係鬼</span></strong>"},{"pid":"15f266cb2460fa9735770fa2b84fbde7e43d491c","tid":1328704,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:03:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【杜絕分化】熱狗惡行 24小時輪流廣播 （2）</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1ccca24f87600f754a0b4f5d4d36414f2540cbcc","tid":1328704,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】</strong></span><br />\n光復香港！沒有暴民，只有暴政！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkVURRBwauKE&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=5a12d807\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化 不捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n七大訴求<br />\n - 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n - 永久完全撤回逃犯條<br />\n - 釋放所有反送中被捕抗爭示威者<br />\n - 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n - 撤回暴動定性<br />\n - 永不實行社會信用評分系統<br />\n - 收回多功能智慧監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8Nr2YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Nr2YF.jpg&h=93a6d743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721! HONGKONGERS! ASSEMBLE!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1327503/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1327503/page/1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1326334/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1326334/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"54b46df2952681e94dd314d95446542739c94098","tid":1328704,"uid":24814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"負皮 完全封鎖<br />\n上一頁"},{"pid":"555c1f1f6e236238bd1f13e933c36e3b0f779625","tid":1328704,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78dedc9488b14695450b38750cf6323a5b262ec7","tid":1328704,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:03:00.000Z","msg":"當睇唔到條撚樣得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n全場除左聽日暴動真係冇撚用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"插撚咗十幾刀都睇唔到？"},{"pid":"fba073381fbf6423b4d59454746ee2c6e2875424","tid":1328704,"uid":118344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:04:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三毛大軍出沒請注意</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設每人一個月30000<br />\n請3000人 一個月先9000萬<br />\n坦白以大陸財力點會冇<br />\n如果3000個全職 一個人開post就全世界衝入去負評/留言<br />\n會唔會lihkg風向就係中聯辦帶動<br />\n我認為我懷疑絕對合理"},{"pid":"0a75027d87e5c8fa32ef2de05cb68687e2312aef","tid":1328704,"u